    </div>
    
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">How do I reset my password?</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600">Click the "Forgot Password" link on the login page and follow the instructions sent to your email. If you don't receive an email within 10 minutes, check your spam folder or contact support.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">When will my commission be paid?</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600">Commissions are processed weekly every Friday for earnings above $25. Payments typically arrive within 1-3 business days depending on your chosen payout method.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">How do I become a brand partner?</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600">Email partnerships@affiliatemarket.com with information about your brand, products, and target commission rates. Our partnerships team will review your application within 48 hours.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Can I promote products on social media?</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600">Yes! You can promote affiliate links on social media, but please follow FTC guidelines by clearly disclosing your affiliate relationship. Use hashtags like #ad or #affiliate.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

